      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i've been having such a hard time sleeping lately like im tossing and turning all night. i already take a bit of melatonin before bed but it isnt really doing much anymore. my doctor recently prescribed me some zolpidem (ambien) for when things get really bad. is it okay if i take both together so i actually get some real sleep? i feel like the melatonin might help the ambien work better.",
